org.osmdroid.wms

Class WMSTileSource

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.osmdroid.tileprovider.tilesource.BitmapTileSourceBase
      • org.osmdroid.tileprovider.tilesource.OnlineTileSourceBase
        • org.osmdroid.wms.WMSTileSource
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    org.osmdroid.tileprovider.tilesource.ITileSource

    public class WMSTileSource
extends org.osmdroid.tileprovider.tilesource.OnlineTileSourceBase
    WMS Map Source. Use this in conjunction with the WMSParser.

    This class is known to work with GeoServer, but only supports a subset of possible WMS configurations.

    Since:
    6.0.0 11/5/15.
    See Also:
    https://github.com/osmdroid/osmdroid/issues/177
